This is more important.

16:18.244 --> 16:20.110
(tires screeching)

16:23.048 --> 16:25.683
Angela!
Open up in there!

16:25.685 --> 16:27.785
(motor running)

16:32.157 --> 16:34.625
Oh, my God!

16:40.966 --> 16:43.167
Angela! Angela, wake up!

16:44.703 --> 16:46.170
What the... Griffin?

16:46.172 --> 16:49.106
Angela, what the hell are you
doin' tryin' to kill yourself?

16:49.108 --> 16:52.142
Oh, why the hell did you
pull me out of there?

16:52.144 --> 16:54.011
You should've just
left me alone!

16:54.013 --> 16:56.080
That's how I'm gonna
end up, anyway.

16:56.082 --> 16:57.348
What are you talkin' about?

16:57.350 --> 16:58.716
I'm talking about the fact

16:58.718 --> 17:01.018
