to live for.

17:01.020 --> 17:02.052
Sure, you do.

17:02.054 --> 17:04.555
Someday, a white man's gonna
be elected president again.

17:04.557 --> 17:08.859
Griffin, I haven't been
with anyone in ten years.

17:08.861 --> 17:10.828
And when you spurned
my advances,

17:10.830 --> 17:12.029
it was a wake-up call.

17:12.031 --> 17:14.665
No one's ever gonna
love me again.

17:14.667 --> 17:15.499
Wait a minute.

17:15.501 --> 17:18.435
So that's why you been actin'
