what it feels like.

17:23.909 --> 17:24.975
I always imagined
it felt very painful.

17:24.977 --> 17:27.878
You just sorta grit your teeth
and let us do what we want.

17:27.880 --> 17:32.049
I just wish one person was able
to find me attractive.

17:32.051 --> 17:35.419
That's not too much
